/*!
    \page strules-pseudo-variable-reference.html
    \title Pseudo Variables
    \previouspage Metadata Generation
    \nextpage Examples

    
    \section1 BUILD_MKSPEC
    
    Specifies a subdirectory path based on toolkit mkspec shortname. In case of Qt-based project, 
    this path will be suffixed by the Qt version used.
    
    For example, for a 64-bit application built on Visual C++ 12.0, using Qt 5.6.3 modules:
    
    \snippet doc_src_strules-manual.pro  BUILD_MKSPEC reference
    
    
    \section1 DELIVERY

    Specifies the absolute path to installation package root directory, i.e. \tt {${\l {PACKAGE}}/Delivery}.


    \section1 PACKAGE

    Specifies the absolute path to package containing current project.

    See also \l {Projects Package}.
*/    


